            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>To Lucius Aelius Caesar, son of Imperator Trajan Hadrianus Augustus, pontifex maximus, holder of tribunician power for the 21st time, imperator for the 2nd time, consul for the 3rd time, father of the fatherland, grandson of of the divine Trajan (conqueror of) Parthia, great-grandson of the divine Nerva, holder of tribunician power and consul for the 2nd time.</p>
